{
  "stem": "24409.11",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides, before it was put in [INAUDIBLE], I was involved in finding and bringing into prisoners of war camps if I can establish where-- where they are, people who had taken part in the beatings [INAUDIBLE] shooting of American flyers.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "American flyers, when they parachuted, where they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was an order after this from the gestapo, from the [INAUDIBLE], from the SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had order to kill him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went into the little villages to inquire where-- we knew where the-- where the planes had run down to find out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I established especially who was involved in [INAUDIBLE] into American [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't follow it up anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One place was very funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I came to a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the town-- a little place about 60 or 80 miles northwest of Frankfurt where flyers had gone down.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we assumed that they are being killed because they was not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went to the burgermeister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by that time, they had gotten rid of the Nazis and then put in power others, supposedly anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes, this was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes, they were [INAUDIBLE] Nazis [? still. ?] And eventually, the burgermeister told you, I understand that a flyer was hit here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, you got data from him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I asked him, what happened to the man who hit him?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said, the man who killed him is-- is dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, how do you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, what's the proof that he is dead?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, he was the only chief of the local police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he shot him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, who can-- who knows about that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Any of the [INAUDIBLE] knows about it because everybody [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Said, all the Poles know about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
